CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 17, reads: "8. Kingsley Carey and Herbert Baruch, local representatives of the Calvert Distillers Company, co-sponsors of the Home Fair wedding, pass out souvenirs from their booth..."
TitMainTitle: Kingsley Carey and Herbert Baruch behind Calvert Distillers Company booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
